# =============================================================================

# Docker Build Context Exclusions for Political Sphere

#

# This file specifies which files should be excluded from the Docker build

# context to improve build performance and reduce image size.

#

# Best Practices:

# - Exclude large files that aren't needed in the container

# - Exclude sensitive files (credentials, secrets)

# - Exclude build artifacts and caches

# - Include only what's necessary for the build

# =============================================================================

