# Notes

# =============================================================================

#

# This .dockerignore file is optimized for:

# - Fast Docker builds (excluding unnecessary files)

# - Smaller image sizes (excluding large assets)

# - Security (excluding secrets and sensitive files)

#

# To verify what's being included in builds:

# docker build --no-cache -t test-build .

# docker history test-build

# docker run --rm test-build ls -la

